 a three-vortex one, and\nso on. The dynamical manifestation of the instabilities mentioned above is\nexamined through direct numerical simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Aug 2012 17:43:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-03"}
