dle arrangement, the spectrum of the VLD varies (at different\ntemperatures) from $\\omega ^{1/3}$ to $\\omega ^{-5/3}$ dependencies. This\nconclusion may serve as a basis for the experimental determination of what kind\nof the turbulence is implemented in different types of generation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Aug 2012 04:22:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
